body:
Turns out it not only causes a failure on gcc 4.8 but also on existing builds, for example [this one]( https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/pytorch-builds/job/pytorch-linux-xenial-cuda9-cudnn7-py3-build/12226/console).

No idea how this got in master in the first place, but this PR fixes it.
